1
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,960
Third Concubine

2
00:01:17,440 --> 00:01:19,000
Liu Xing was only an accomplice

3
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:22,160
And you are the real murderer

4
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:27,040
I knew you'd come to Lu Quan again

5
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,600
So I set a trap

6
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:29,800
To lure you in

7
00:01:31,920 --> 00:01:35,200
You made up the Fox Spirit rumor too, didn't you?

8
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:38,560
Those fox bones were only a few years old

9
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,840
Not some hundred-year Fox Spirit at all

10
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:44,880
You used the Fox Spirit rumor and poisoned with
Soul-Bewitching Herb

11
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:48,240
All to stage a Fox Spirit murder case

12
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:53,280
First, you poisoned the Matriarch and Lu Xin
one after another at home

13
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:56,240
To make everyone think it was a Fox Spirit's curse

14
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,840
Then you came to me

15
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,600
Lying that you wanted the fox's bones collected

16
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:02,800
And used tools to imitate a fox's cry

17
00:02:03,520 --> 00:02:07,200
Then used a fox mask to fake the Fox Spirit's haunting

18
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:09,880
But the age of the fox bones didn't match

19
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,480
As a Bone Collector

20
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,240
I could tell at a glance

21
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,880
To find a scapegoat

22
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:19,160
You seduced Liu Xing into becoming your accomplice

23
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:22,600
And ordered him to poison Lu Quan

24
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:26,480
But Xu Nan's antidote saved Lu Quan

25
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:29,080
So you had Liu Xing kidnap her

26
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,360
And even tried to kill her

27
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:32,400
But because we showed up

28
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,720
Liu Xing was exposed

29
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,880
You killed him to silence him

30
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:38,960
That's not how it was

31
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,680
Please, listen to my explanation

32
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,120
It was Liu Xing

33
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,640
Liu Xing only wanted to seize the Lu Family's fortune

34
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,120
He forced me to do it

35
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,920
Stop pretending. My uncle is an idiot

36
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,680
He could never have planned something like this

37
00:02:54,480 --> 00:02:58,480
Third Concubine, to swallow up our Lu Family's fortune

38
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,200
You killed my eldest aunt

39
00:03:00,200 --> 00:03:01,120
And my brother

40
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:03,360
How vicious you are

41
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:06,440
Lu Quan, it's true she did all this

42
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,440
But everything she did

43
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:10,640
Was not for the Lu Family's fortune

44
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,200
Then...

45
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,760
It was for Lu Ze

46
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:20,000
The Lu Family also has a man away in the army, Lu Ze

47
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:21,120
Who is Lu Ze?

48
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:23,880
Master Lu's nephew

49
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:25,280
Yes

50
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,120
It was all for A Ze

51
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,800
That year, I was sold into the Lu Family

52
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,880
They never treated me like a human being

53
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:37,480
If you must blame someone, blame your useless womb

54
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:40,120
It was A Ze

55
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,040
He knew my joys and sorrows

56
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,000
He gave me hope to go on living

57
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:51,120
Though I bear the surname Lu

58
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,080
This house was never truly mine

59
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:58,640
From now on, offend the Matriarch less

60
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,120
Not long after

61
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:05,200
A Ze was forced by the master to join the army

62
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:08,720
After that, we had no contact

63
00:04:09,720 --> 00:04:11,080
Until some time ago

64
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:13,080
A Ze suddenly sent me a letter

65
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:15,320
Saying he would return next month

66
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,480
For our future

67
00:04:18,280 --> 00:04:20,360
The entire Lu Family had to disappear

68
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:26,920
We found this in Liu Xing's room

69
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,880
This was all just his scheme

70
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:34,640
He copied Lu Ze's handwriting to write this letter

71
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:48,960
And this telegram too

72
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:53,800
Lu Ze died in battle a year ago

73
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:58,480
Everything you're doing now

74
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,280
Is only causing needless bloodshed

75
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,080
A Ze

76
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:29,240
A Ze, A Ze

77
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:33,880
A Ze

78
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:36,320
How could this happen?

79
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,800
No, no, it can't be

80
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:40,920
How could A Ze...

81
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,800
A Ze

82
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:49,040
Everything I planned for you was for nothing

83
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,160
A Ze

84
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:01,000
A Ze

85
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,240
I'm coming to be with you now

86
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,360
No

87
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:11,920
No

88
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:27,040
Then he'll never be apart from me again

89
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,600
Let's stop here

90
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,760
I never thought a spoiled young master like you

91
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:47,000
would willingly donate all your estate to an orphanage

92
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,840
The Lu Family and the Wang Family colluded for years

93
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,440
All of it was ill-gotten wealth

94
00:06:51,160 --> 00:06:53,800
Donating it counts as doing one good deed

95
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:55,880
Human nature...

96
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:59,520
is often ugly in the face of money

97
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,920
Right now, I just want to stay far from all this trouble

98
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:04,920
Then what do you plan to do next?

99
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:06,720
The world is wide

100
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,280
I want to go try my luck in Beiping

101
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,520
and see if there's anything I truly like doing

102
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:14,880
That's great. I hope all goes well for you, Young Master Lu

103
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,200
and that you make something of yourself

104
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,280
I'll take that blessing

105
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:20,920
Who knows when we'll meet again after this

106
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,640
Give me a hug

107
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,320
Okay

108
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,600
Be careful of the Wang Family

109
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:36,680
Don't worry, I've made every preparation

110
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,960
Until we meet again

111
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,800
Until we meet again

112
00:07:49,760 --> 00:07:51,280
You should head back

113
00:08:11,280 --> 00:08:13,640
Master, the Fifth Concubine even went to see Lu Quan

114
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,520
I heard she was the one who saved Lu Quan

115
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,400
Lu Quan's loose mouth may have already

116
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,880
So what if she knows?

117
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,960
I saw through her long ago

118
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:29,360
She married into our Wang Family for other motives

119
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:33,520
For now, let her stir up all the trouble she wants

120
00:08:34,560 --> 00:08:35,800
Once the time is right

121
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,600
I'll naturally have a way to deal with her

122
00:08:40,680 --> 00:08:41,200
Master

123
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:42,560
They've sent over another one

124
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:46,440
Behave yourself

125
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:53,960
Move, move
